### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/healthz

### Readiness
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/readyz

### Metrics
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/metrics

### List cars
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cars

### Create car
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plate_number": "06-AYBU-02",
  "make": "Ford",
  "model": "Focus",
  "year": 2024,
  "location": "Ankara Downtown",
  "daily_rate": 1500
}

### List customers
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/customers

### Create customer
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Ada Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@example.com",
  "phone": "+90 312 000 0000"
}

### Create rental
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/rentals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "car_id": 1,
  "customer_id": 1,
  "start_date": "2026-05-20",
  "end_date": "2026-05-22"
}

### Return rental
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/rentals/1/return

